(1, 77, 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet', 'lorem-ipsum-dolor-sit-amet', '<p>Nullam pharetra massa at erat semper, eu faucibus mauris varius. </p>', '', 1, 2, '2015-09-17 09:22:04', 951, '', '2015-09-17 09:22:04', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-17 09:22:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 1, '', '', 1, 42, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(2, 93, 'Our Story', 'out-story', '<table class="our-story">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4>About Shevron Pte Ltd</h4>\r\n<p>Shevron Pte Ltd has proved to be the innovative one stop provider of customized embroidery, silkscreen, greeting cards, customised gifts and apparels maker. It is the first and only company in Singapore to infuse embroidery into high quality products such as cards, corporate products and Lunar New Year decorations.</p>\r\n<h4>Design Excellence</h4>\r\n<p>Our dynamic design team is experienced in embellishing clients'' ideas into the most creative and cost-effective designs. The team also bears in mind all aspects of the production process which ensures that designs are applicable to all products and consistency is achieved across all our merchandise.</p>\r\n<h4>Manufacturing Excellence</h4>\r\n<p>Shevron''s products are produced by our associate company, Sam Embroidery - renowned for its distinctive manufacturing styles and impressive embroidery techniques since the early 80s. The world-class embroidery machinery used by Sam Embroidery further gives our products a stitch above the rest.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_story/our_story_1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_story/our_story_2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4>Quality of Materials</h4>\r\n<p>Instrumental in the production of Shevron''s embroidery products are the thread and the cloth. We employ ISACORD thread from Germany and a wide plethora of fabric such as the Eco-Fi felt, the duchess satin and the organza just to bring to you products of the finest and highest quality. To further adorn our products, we creatively employ bold colours and decorative materials such as sequins as well, to satisfy every customer''s individual and unique taste.</p>\r\n<h4>International Distribution</h4>\r\n<p>Shevron cards and premiums are sold in countries including Singapore, Australia, Brunei, Canada, Hong Kong, Finland, Taiwan, United Kingdom, USA and more.</p>\r\n<h4>Manufacturing Excellence</h4>\r\n<p>Shevron Pte Ltd has proved to be the innovative one stop provider of customized embroidery, silkscreen, greeting cards, customised gifts and apparels maker. It is the first and only company in Singapore to infuse embroidery into high quality products such as cards, corporate products and Lunar New Year decorations.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 8, '2015-09-29 02:15:14', 951, '', '2015-10-28 02:50:10', 951, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-29 02:15:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/article\\/our_story\\/our_story_1.jpg","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 2, '', '', 1, 70, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(3, 94, 'Our Services', 'our-services', '<h4>Embroidery Services</h4>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>You name it, we stitch it! It''s that simple! Whether it is simple T-shirt logo or an intricate embroidered pattern on a dress, with our renowned world-class embroidery techniques and impressive range of high quality thread and &nbsp;material at disposal, all fabric products can be made into a embroidered item with a corporate identity or a personalised touch. Please feel free to contact us regarding any of your special embroidery needs.</p>\r\n<h4>Product Design</h4>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_6.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_7.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/our_services/our_services_8.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Starting from the barest of ideas all the way to a straightforward aesthetic ideation, our design team is experienced in marrying a creative vision of what a finished product will look like with a deep understanding of the technical aspects of production and the properties of the material and medium used. Whatever limitations or requests you have, our design team is capable of delivering cost-effective and innovative products that fulfill or even exceed your expectations.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2015-09-29 02:16:18', 951, '', '2015-10-28 02:52:04', 951, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-29 02:16:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_1.jpg","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 1, '', '', 1, 23, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(4, 95, 'Customisation', 'customisation', '<p style="text-align: center;">Like what you''ve seen so far? Do you have an idea of your own that you want to turn into a beautiful embroidered reality? Or do you simply wish to customise or personalise an existing model from our product range? Our customisation service might be just right for you. When you choose our customisation service, you embard on a magical journey to play a pivotal role in the creation of your own embroidered piece.</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="2"><img src="images/article/customisation/customisation-1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/customisation/customisation-2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="images/article/customisation/customisation-3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">You can start by browsing through our corporate products listed in our <a href="index.php?option=com_shevron&amp;view=product&amp;Itemid=114">products</a> page or our own Shervon''s products listed in our <a href="index.php?option=com_customfilters&amp;view=products&amp;Itemid=116">shop online</a> page. Upon seeing anything that caught your fancy that you want to customise, simply click the enquire or customise button that come with the product''s detail page, filled in the enquiry form and send it to us. Or maybe you already have something in mind and you wish to contact us immediately, simply click on the button below.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2015-09-29 02:16:43', 951, '', '2015-10-28 02:52:44', 951, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-29 02:16:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"images\\/article\\/customisation\\/customisation-2.jpg","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 8, 0, '', '', 1, 62, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
