(39, 2, 1, '', '2015-10-28 02:50:10', 951, 4154, '59c3aa5886d9802c9fa6474f00aaa849f1764558', '{"id":2,"asset_id":"93","title":"Our Story","alias":"out-story","introtext":"<table class=\\"our-story\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>\\r\\n<h4>About Shevron Pte Ltd<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Shevron Pte Ltd has proved to be the innovative one stop provider of customized embroidery, silkscreen, greeting cards, customised gifts and apparels maker. It is the first and only company in Singapore to infuse embroidery into high quality products such as cards, corporate products and Lunar New Year decorations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>Design Excellence<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Our dynamic design team is experienced in embellishing clients'' ideas into the most creative and cost-effective designs. The team also bears in mind all aspects of the production process which ensures that designs are applicable to all products and consistency is achieved across all our merchandise.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>Manufacturing Excellence<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Shevron''s products are produced by our associate company, Sam Embroidery - renowned for its distinctive manufacturing styles and impressive embroidery techniques since the early 80s. The world-class embroidery machinery used by Sam Embroidery further gives our products a stitch above the rest.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_story\\/our_story_1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_story\\/our_story_2.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td>\\r\\n<h4>Quality of Materials<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Instrumental in the production of Shevron''s embroidery products are the thread and the cloth. We employ ISACORD thread from Germany and a wide plethora of fabric such as the Eco-Fi felt, the duchess satin and the organza just to bring to you products of the finest and highest quality. To further adorn our products, we creatively employ bold colours and decorative materials such as sequins as well, to satisfy every customer''s individual and unique taste.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>International Distribution<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Shevron cards and premiums are sold in countries including Singapore, Australia, Brunei, Canada, Hong Kong, Finland, Taiwan, United Kingdom, USA and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>Manufacturing Excellence<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Shevron Pte Ltd has proved to be the innovative one stop provider of customized embroidery, silkscreen, greeting cards, customised gifts and apparels maker. It is the first and only company in Singapore to infuse embroidery into high quality products such as cards, corporate products and Lunar New Year decorations.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-09-29 02:15:14","created_by":"951","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-10-28 02:50:10","modified_by":"951","checked_out":"951","checked_out_time":"2015-10-28 02:48:13","publish_up":"2015-09-29 02:15:14","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/article\\\\\\/our_story\\\\\\/our_story_1.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":5,"ordering":"2","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"54","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(40, 3, 1, '', '2015-10-28 02:52:04', 951, 3581, 'a83e7a5314dc923d488218be9ae5bee0c9892211', '{"id":3,"asset_id":"94","title":"Our Services","alias":"our-services","introtext":"<h4>Embroidery Services<\\/h4>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_2.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_3.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_4.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p>You name it, we stitch it! It''s that simple! Whether it is simple T-shirt logo or an intricate embroidered pattern on a dress, with our renowned world-class embroidery techniques and impressive range of high quality thread and &nbsp;material at disposal, all fabric products can be made into a embroidered item with a corporate identity or a personalised touch. Please feel free to contact us regarding any of your special embroidery needs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>Product Design<\\/h4>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_5.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_6.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_7.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/our_services\\/our_services_8.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p>Starting from the barest of ideas all the way to a straightforward aesthetic ideation, our design team is experienced in marrying a creative vision of what a finished product will look like with a deep understanding of the technical aspects of production and the properties of the material and medium used. Whatever limitations or requests you have, our design team is capable of delivering cost-effective and innovative products that fulfill or even exceed your expectations.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-09-29 02:16:18","created_by":"951","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-10-28 02:52:04","modified_by":"951","checked_out":"951","checked_out_time":"2015-10-28 02:51:28","publish_up":"2015-09-29 02:16:18","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/article\\\\\\/our_services\\\\\\/our_services_1.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":10,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"23","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":