(41, 4, 1, '', '2015-10-28 02:52:44', 951, 3239, 'a70dff58ccf211f577bf0525cfd51fbb300ace6c', '{"id":4,"asset_id":"95","title":"Customisation","alias":"customisation","introtext":"<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Like what you''ve seen so far? Do you have an idea of your own that you want to turn into a beautiful embroidered reality? Or do you simply wish to customise or personalise an existing model from our product range? Our customisation service might be just right for you. When you choose our customisation service, you embard on a magical journey to play a pivotal role in the creation of your own embroidered piece.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td rowspan=\\"2\\"><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/customisation\\/customisation-1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/customisation\\/customisation-2.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"images\\/article\\/customisation\\/customisation-3.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">You can start by browsing through our corporate products listed in our <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_shevron&amp;view=product&amp;Itemid=114\\">products<\\/a> page or our own Shervon''s products listed in our <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_customfilters&amp;view=products&amp;Itemid=116\\">shop online<\\/a> page. Upon seeing anything that caught your fancy that you want to customise, simply click the enquire or customise button that come with the product''s detail page, filled in the enquiry form and send it to us. Or maybe you already have something in mind and you wish to contact us immediately, simply click on the button below.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-09-29 02:16:43","created_by":"951","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-10-28 02:52:44","modified_by":"951","checked_out":"951","checked_out_time":"2015-10-28 02:52:12","publish_up":"2015-09-29 02: